5021f0f81bd1b7a15d7e5f02d108f4f230a8f737.query:
SELECT
                discord_id,
                language as "language: DbLanguage",
                gender as "gender: DbGender",
                insert_tm,
                update_tm
            FROM users
            WHERE discord_id = $1

d24a479da7a5fec81bb1c6f9996a708638b05c58.query:
SELECT
                discord_id,
                language as "language: DbLanguage",
                gender as "gender: DbGender",
                prefix,
                insert_tm,
                update_tm
            FROM guilds
            WHERE discord_id = $1

e4684c3a29bf72eda8b131afe154220bef2745c8.query:
INSERT INTO users (discord_id, language, gender, insert_tm, update_tm)
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $4)
            ON CONFLICT (discord_id) DO UPDATE
            SET discord_id = $1, language = $2, gender = $3, update_tm = $4

f074285e6893c9a7b00c07a92fff8a891e16946d.query:
INSERT INTO guilds (discord_id, language, gender, prefix, insert_tm, update_tm)
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $5)
            ON CONFLICT (discord_id) DO UPDATE
            SET discord_id = $1, language = $2, gender = $3, prefix = $4, update_tm = $5
